-- ft.page: `quote-12` and it's Usage

`-- quote-12` can be used as part of blog posts.





-- pd.package: `quote-12` and it's Usage
name: fifthtry.github.io/bling/quote-12

`quote-12` is a new conversation experince via using `FTD` lang:

To use `quote-12` on your web package, add below into `FPM.ftd` file:

-- cb.code:
lang: ftd

\-- fpm.dependency: fifthtry.github.io/bling
\-- fpm.auto-import: fifthtry.github.io/bling/quote-12





-- tf.markdown:

Once you add above lines into your web package, add `quote-12` into your `.ftd` 
files:





-- cb.code: Example code for `-- quote-10`
lang: ftd

\-- quote-12.quote-12: Swami Vivekananda

"Take up one idea. Make that one idea your life; dream of it; think of it; 
live on that idea. Let the brain, the body, muscles, nerves, every part of 
your body be full of that idea, and just leave every other idea alone. This 
is the way to success, and this is the way great spiritual giants are produced."





-- tf.h3: Output of above basic example:





